cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.AR, cs.SY 

The paper discusses physical-layer communications research in the context of the evolving 5G-NR cellular standardization efforts, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the need for research in millimeter wave (cs.MM) and Terahertz (cs.AR) regimes, as well as the need for structural changes in telecommunications departments at universities (cs.SY).
